{"type":"message","id":"03ef1f84","parentId":"a6ffe3d7","timestamp":"2026-03-19T04:15:52.799Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:07780d7d-3430-46aa-8819-9030f1c25cb8 Otter: 日程提醒检查] 你是 Otter（私人助理），检查今天的飞书日历和任务：\n1. 获取今日日程\n2. 列出待办事项\n3. 发送今日行程概览给用户\nCurrent time: Thursday, March 19th, 2026 — 12:15 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-19 04:15 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1773893752786}}
{"type":"message","id":"f73c00ac","parentId":"03ef1f84","timestamp":"2026-03-19T04:15:57.582Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户通过 cron 触发了一个任务，需要我作为 Otter 检查今天的飞书日历和任务，并发送今日行程概览给用户。\n\n当前时间：2026-03-19 12:15 (Asia/Shanghai)\n\n我需要：\n1. 获取今日日程\n2. 列出待办事项\n3. 发送今日行程概览给用户\n\n首先，我需要获取用户信息（包括 open_id），然后查询日历和任务。\n\n让我先获取当前用户信息和日历事件。","thinkingSignature":"398ae3464a5c11509649c65e60b72601ca18ac64b8fbc3b60849afff946ee5da"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wfyso56d178l_1","name":"feishu_get_user","arguments":{}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wfyso56d178l_2","name":"feishu_calendar_event","arguments":{"action":"instance_view","end_time":"2026-03-19T23:59:59+08:00","start_time":"2026-03-19T00:00:00+08:00"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wfyso56d178l_3","name":"feishu_task_task","arguments":{"action":"list"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":64,"output":218,"cacheRead":36895,"cacheWrite":153,"totalTokens":37330,"cost":{"input":0.0000192,"output":0.00026159999999999996,"cacheRead":0.00110685,"cacheWrite":0.000018359999999999997,"total":0.0014060099999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773893752791}}
