{"type":"message","id":"729bc6e7","parentId":"7097e235","timestamp":"2026-03-19T04:16:06.137Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看来需要用户授权才能访问日历和任务。我需要告知用户需要授权，或者使用其他方式。但作为 cron 任务，我应该直接返回需要授权的提示。\n\n让我用消息工具发送一条消息给用户，说明需要授权才能查看日历和任务。","thinkingSignature":"c9dc2f05bf6efb97812b649b31d3ee3750fd11eadbdd8b796a41dfea7e79d70c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_nxcr6mdk27ek_1","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","message":"📋 **今日行程概览**\n\n⚠️ **需要授权**：Otter 需要获取您的日历和任务权限才能显示今日行程。\n\n请运行 `/feishu_oauth` 授权后，我将为您展示：\n- 📅 今日日程安排\n- ✅ 待办任务清单\n\n给您带来不便，敬请谅解！"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":1112,"output":152,"cacheRead":36895,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38159,"cost":{"input":0.0003336,"output":0.0001824,"cacheRead":0.00110685,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00162285}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773893762172}}
